org.openimaj.data.identity

Interface Identifiable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IdentifiableObject, VFSGroupDataset, VFSListDataset

    public interface Identifiable
    An Identifiable is an object that has an associated identifier. Two instances of Identifiable with the same identifier should be considered equal.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
